            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1678882035851-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>remaining sliced spring greens</strong> to a large piece of <strong>tin foil</strong> (or two!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Scrunch the edges of the foil to form a sealed parcel[s] and add to a baking tray</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 10-12 min or until the spring greens are tender – these are your <strong>buttery spring greens</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
